description.text: This list is created from multiple authors and sources. With varying routes, names and descriptions, it can be hard to identify which routes from each source describe the same problem. This list depicts every described climb from all sources along with their most likely match from other sources. The "match confidence" is logged to deal with some uncertainty. This list doens't include the author's descriptions, topos or maps, so discrepancies will be listed under match confidence.

Should be noted I never intended this list to be used as a definative guide. It's simply the data collection for a possible app. The app would exclude many redundant or less notable climbs, but allow user's to alter their filters to display them. So this list includes a lot of garbage.

This list is still in the works. The Garden Main has been logged, but data from NextAscent isn't fully logged yet. Updates from other guides will be added as well. For major issues, I'll need to talk with some of the authors.
